videos.headline: Sumlin, Jones express vastly different tones postgame
videos.description: Kevin Sumlin and Butch Jones look back on the range of emotions during Texas A&M's double overtime win over Tennessee.

videos.headline: Tennessee's loss means door opens for Florida in SEC East
videos.description: Heather Dinich explains how Tennessee's loss is a big blow to their aspirations of winning the SEC East with Alabama lurking.
